OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,FA man who created multiple fake social
OL,7,Fmedia accounts to stalk his ex-
OL,8,Fgirlfriend sent her an alarming
OL,9,Fmessage that he was "only 50 yards
OL,10,Faway" from her at an event.
OL,12,FLiverpool Crown Court heard how the
OL,13,Fvictim ended a relationship with
OL,14,FRobert Forshaw, 42, after five weeks,
OL,15,Fwhen she observed controlling
OL,16,Fbehaviours from him.
