OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,FIn December 2023, Forshaw began a
OL,7,Fcampaign to discredit the victim, with
OL,8,Fthe court hearing how he made numerous
OL,9,Fcalls to her from withheld numbers and
OL,10,Fsent her abusive emails.
OL,12,FHe also contacted her workplace
OL,13,Fpretending to be the partner of one of
OL,14,Fher clients and accused her of
OL,15,Finappropriate behaviour towards the
OL,16,Fclient.
