OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,FForshaw then created a network of fake
OL,7,Fsocial media accounts and used these
OL,8,Fto publish more content about the
OL,9,Fvictim, going so far as to send
OL,10,Fmessages between each of the accounts
OL,11,Fhe had created, discussing her and
OL,12,Fmaking false allegations about her.
OL,13,FForshaw then screenshotted these and
OL,14,Femailed them to the victim.
OL,16,FIn late January 2024, a friend of the
OL,17,Fvictim posted images of them on social
OL,18,Fmedia attending a sporting event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
