OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,FThe court heard how Forshaw had also
OL,7,Fattended the event and later used one
OL,8,Fof the fake accounts he had created to
OL,9,Fcomment on the post, saying "I'm only
OL,10,F50 yards away from you".
OL,12,FAfter the series of incidents were
OL,13,Freported to Cheshire Police, an
OL,14,Finvestigation was launched and
OL,15,FForshaw, knowing he was a person of
OL,16,Finterest, concealed his devices -
OL,17,Fadmitted his ploy to a third party,
OL,18,Fwho then told police.
