OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,FDespite Forshaw's best efforts,
OL,7,Fofficers were able to piece together
OL,8,Fhis digital footprint and attribute
OL,9,Fthe numerous fake social media
OL,10,Faccounts and email addresses to him.
OL,12,FDespite this Forshaw continued to deny
OL,13,Fany responsibility and a trial was set
OL,14,Ffor July 2025.
OL,16,FBut, on the first day of the trial, he
OL,17,Fchanged his plea to guilty.
OL,19,FForshaw, of Bewsey and Whitecross,
OL,20,FWarrington, admitted stalking
OL,21,Finvolving serious alarm or distress.
