OL,6,FHe was jailed for two years and nine
OL,7,Fmonths.
OL,9,FHe was also handed a 10 year
OL,10,FRestraining Order prohibiting him from
OL,11,Fcontacting the victim, publishing
OL,12,Fanything about her, or entering
OL,13,Fmultiple areas of Warrington and
OL,14,FWidnes.
