OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing,
OL,7,Finvestigating officer Police Constable
OL,8,FCharl Ashmore of the Harm Reduction
OL,9,FUnit said: "Robert Forshaw is a serial
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse perpetrator and this
OL,11,Fconviction clearly demonstrates that
OL,12,Fhe is either incapable or unwilling to
OL,13,Faccept his victim's decision to end
OL,14,Ftheir relationship with him.
OL,16,F"Forshaw clearly hoped that by hiding
OL,17,Fbehind a screen, he could punish the
OL,18,Fvictim for calling out his behaviours
OL,19,Fand subsequently ending their
OL,20,Frelationship without repercussions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
