OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,F"However, he, like many stalkers,
OL,7,Ffailed to account for his digital
OL,8,Ffootprint, which led investigating
OL,9,Fofficers straight to him. This again
OL,10,Fproves that the internet offers no
OL,11,Fsanctuary to those who wish to commit
OL,12,Fviolence against women and girls and
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse.
