OL,3,C'I'm only 50 yards away': Stalker used
OL,4,Cfake account to send chilling message
OL,6,F"His behaviour and offending have
OL,7,Funderstandably left his victim
OL,8,Fphysically shaken and emotionally
OL,9,Fdistressed. That said, the strength
OL,10,Fshe has shown throughout this
OL,11,Finvestigation, right up to the moment
OL,12,FForshaw changed his plea, is truly
OL,13,Fcommendable.
OL,15,F"Thanks to her bravery in taking the
OL,16,Fstep to contact police, Forshaw has
OL,17,Fbeen held accountable for his actions
OL,18,Fand is facing a spell behind bars."
